{"tid":128258,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"酒駕對撞雙亡 駕駛雙方竟是父子","createTime":"2017-02-20T16:11:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-21T15:17:55.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be3812f346e53ae407cbe0807592ba44a87566ab","tid":128258,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T16:11:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/02/20/4/3196886.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F02%2F20%2F4%2F3196886.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=e3f791c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國18日凌晨發生兩駕車迎面相撞事故，對撞雙亡的卻碰巧是對父子。圖為布拉席爾父子生前的合照。(取材自臉書)<br />\nfacebook美國阿拉巴馬州費耶特郡（Fayette）一對父子18日凌晨駕車迎面相撞，父親當場死亡，兒子送醫後不治。警方表示，酒駕是這宗悲劇的禍首。<br />\n阿拉巴馬州州警表示，50歲的傑弗瑞‧莫瑞斯‧布拉席爾（Jeffrey Morris Brasher）和22歲兒子奧斯汀‧布雷恩‧布拉席爾（Austin Blaine Brasher）分別駕車於18日凌晨4時10分左右，在費耶特郡49號公路相撞。兩人都住在班克斯頓（Bankston），該鎮在伯明罕以西67哩。<br />\n<br />\n州警說，老布拉席爾駕駛2006年的福特小貨卡，與小布拉席爾駕駛的2004年雪佛蘭小貨卡對撞。<a href=\"http://Al.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAl.com&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHjM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=5f5071a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Al.com</a>網站指出，兩人都未繫安全帶。<br />\n<br />\n州警指出，老布拉席爾在車禍現場死亡，小布拉席爾被送到伯明罕的UAB醫院，至上午9時18分傷重不治。州警表示，將繼續調查車禍肇因，但初步顯示疑與酒駕有關。<br />\n<br />\n他們的家人珍妮佛‧布拉席爾在臉書表達對兩人驟逝的哀痛，珍妮佛貼文寫道：「這一切能不能只是一場噩夢？」她在另一則貼文表示，他們兩人「現在都成了她的守護天使」，並表示「已經開始想念他們」。<br />\n<br />\n另一位家人潘蜜拉‧布拉席爾說，在這樣的悲劇失去兩人，令她份外痛心。她說：「我們的心碎了，但對上帝的信仰不移，同時失去傑弗瑞和奧斯汀的悲痛心情無法言喻，但念及他們仍在一起，稍可告慰。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6810/2295687?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2#prettyPhoto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6810%2F2295687%3Ffrom%3Dudn-catelistnews_ch2%23prettyPhoto&d=3FtZuWe%2BwKi7N9uEGSTnHjM0pwszV1jUpWwTgNsMWwc%3D&h=21377b5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6810/2295687?from=udn-catelistnews_ch2#prettyPhoto</a>"},{"pid":"d4019ce3ae0894e9aba534ee0db0c74aad252bd9","tid":128258,"uid":78473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:07:36.000Z","msg":"虎父無犬子"},{"pid":"074dc64bab8bcb8648592592e7ba5e9353ad9f4b","tid":128258,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:30:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abe220d7b5d15d2ac72e3d0f9c37f11169f6cd49","tid":128258,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0403633782b4fb8d653e69cf63247501671de8d5","tid":128258,"uid":11970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:55:15.000Z","msg":"有冇咁啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa7ee4bce27d717b5a3aea325ad8cdac26873c59","tid":128258,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:57:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adeadf5a559f6f3a5fa8e577d69adbc0702f4fa4","tid":128258,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T17:58:11.000Z","msg":"估錯國家"},{"pid":"2ca7b1e6fb820e43f634348b266b07b1a0c8888e","tid":128258,"uid":31752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:00:01.000Z","msg":"老母最無奈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5477b7dff1504b1efc2c4c912213941101f58e3","tid":128258,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-20T18:00:49.000Z","msg":"垃圾red neck"},{"pid":"c003bc39b18024687f6209207d58cc031aceaf27","tid":128258,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T02:23:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/